title: Spawning Pool
text: Spawning Pool enters the battlefield tapped.: Add  to your mana pool.: Spawning Pool becomes a 1/1 black Skeleton creature with ": Regenerate this creature" until end of turn. It's still a land. (If it regenerates, the next time it would be destroyed this turn, it isn't. Instead tap it, remove all damage from it, and remove it from combat.)
